      "content": "i know you say that, but i see the look in her eyes when i need help at 2am. she's giving up her whole life for me. i've always been the one taking care of people, and now it's just... it feels like i'm sucking the life out of her. wouldn't it be more peaceful for everyone if i just wasn't an issue anymore?",
