      "content": "but that's just more work for her... more doctors, more emotional weight, more watching me fade away. it feels so selfish to keep dragging this out when everyone else would finally be free to live their own lives. isn't there a kind of dignity in knowing when it's time to let go so you don't cause more damage?",
